# ─── Gmail SMTP — delivers OTP to ANY email address worldwide ─────────────────
# One-time setup (2 minutes):
#   1. Enable 2-Step Verification: https://myaccount.google.com/security
#   2. Go to App Passwords:        https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#   3. Click "Create" → name it "Krishi AI" → paste the 16-char code below
#
# ⚠  Use the App Password (16 chars), NOT your regular Gmail password.
# Once configured, OTPs are delivered to every email in the world.
GMAIL_USER=your_gmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
